text: Had a great experience at Sushi Express today. Despite the long queue, Aunt Ng Ai Tee, the checkout cashier, showed exceptional attentiveness and kindness. She noticed my sushi box was dripping water onto my hand and, as soon as it was my turn, the first thing she did was hand me a tissue. Such a small gesture, but it truly made my day! The food was delicious and reasonably priced too. Excellent service and great value‚Äîhighly recommend!

My favourite go to  when I want to eat affordable and good sushi.Their bentos are cheap.and good.
